name: Commander Jane Shepard
description: This model is based on SD 1.5 and is trained on screen shots of the default female face from Mass Effect. This is my 5th attempt at a Femshep model. It still has some issues. Eyes often need work. I think the variability of the eyes in the game confuse the training model. Either way, it was fun to make. Hopefully you enjoy it too.
